name: easy to love hard to forget
description:
The artwork story :
I really wanted to forget,
that we had ever met.
But you are clinging too tight,
haunting my lonely nights.
I tried to go to places so far from here,
yet its still your voice I want to hear.
Your face and smile I want to see,
its always with you I want to be.
Hope you'll be the one for me,
because I can't afford to set you free.
Though we are a thousand miles apart,
you'll still be the one in my heart.
